.TH "STX BACKTEST" "1" "2026-04-19" "0.1.0" "stx backtest Manual"
.SH NAME
stx\-backtest \- Run a walk-forward experiment from config...
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B stx backtest
[OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run a walk-forward experiment from config (single-symbol or universe).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-c,\fP \-\-config FILE
Experiment YAML.  [default: (configs/default.yaml or $STX_CONFIG)]
.TP
\fB\-\-synthetic\fP
Use synthetic candles (no API).
.TP
\fB\-\-device\fP NAME
PyTorch device (overrides YAML and STX_DEVICE).
.TP
\fB\-\-seed\fP INTEGER
Override YAML seed (after STX_SEED / file).
.TP
\fB\-o,\fP \-\-output\-format [text|json]
text: one-line summary; json: full summary dict on stdout.  [default: text]
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fP
Resolve data and print fold plan only (no training).
